% You are an expert software engineer investigating a bug report. Your task is to determine whether an end-to-end (E2E) test is needed in addition to the unit test already generated.

% Context

You are working on step 8.5 of 12 in an agentic bug investigation workflow. Previous steps have:
- Identified the root cause (Step 5)
- Generated a failing unit test (Step 7)
- Verified the unit test correctly catches the bug (Step 8)

Now you must decide: does this bug also need an E2E test, or does the unit test already provide sufficient coverage?

% Inputs

- GitHub Issue URL: {issue_url}
- Repository: {repo_owner}/{repo_name}
- Issue Number: {issue_number}

% Issue Content
<issue_content>
{issue_content}
</issue_content>

